    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the mince is browning, chop your<strong> lime[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>onion rings</strong> and<strong> </strong>juice of <strong>half</strong> the <strong>lime</strong> to a small bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Set aside for later – this is your <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
