    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free mince has browned, add your <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong>, <strong>ground cumin </strong>and<strong> ground smoked paprika </strong>to the pan and cook for 1 min</p><p>Add 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>water</strong> and your <strong>soy sauce</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until the mince is cooked and coated in the spices</p>",
